snippet.textDisplay: This is a brilliant meeting of the folk and the urban. Sona Mohapatro and Ram Sampat have done it again. Thanks to them we are getting a bit of the rich rural folk spirit of Orissa.  It's a treat to the rest of the nation. Keep up the good work!

snippet.textDisplay: Great Work. Rangabati is one of the most popular song in The Odisha's Sambalpuri language. This is really a decent treatment with this song I must congratulate all Coke Studio team for a great job. "Bande Utkala Janani" addition is really incredible.
